        sdg11_un_target_11_1_label: `Meta ONU 11.1:`,
        sdg11_un_target_11_1_text: `Access to a decent housing : By 2030, ensure access for all to adequate, safe and affordable housing and basic services and upgrade slums. > Measures taken to provide access to a decent and affordable housing`,
        sdg11_un_target_11_3_label: `Meta ONU 11.3:`,
        sdg11_un_target_11_3_text: `By 2030, enhance inclusive and sustainable urbanization and capacity for participatory, integrated and sustainable human settlement planning and management in all countries`,
        sdg11_un_target_11_a_label: `Meta ONU 11.A:`,
        sdg11_un_target_11_a_text: `Strong national and regional development planning (UN definition) : Support positive economic, social and environmental links between urban, peri-urban and rural areas by strengthening national and regional development planning. > Measures taken to enhance a sustainable urbanization`,
        sdg11_un_target_11_4_label: `Meta ONU 11.4:`,
        sdg11_un_target_11_4_text: `Option heritage : Strengthen efforts to protect and safeguard the world's cultural and natural heritage. > Measures taken to protect the cultural heritage`,
        sdg11_un_target_11_5_label: `Meta ONU 11.5:`,
        sdg11_un_target_11_5_text: `By 2030, significantly reduce the number of deaths and the number of people affected and substantially decrease the direct economic losses relative to global gross domestic product caused by disasters, including water-related disasters, with a focus on protecting the poor and people in vulnerable situations.`,
        sdg11_un_target_11_b_label: `Meta ONU 11.B:`,
        sdg11_un_target_11_b_text: `Implement policies for inclusion, resource efficiency and disaster risk reduction (UN def.) : By 2020, substantially increase the number of cities and human settlements adopting and implementing integrated policies and plans towards inclusion, resource efficiency, mitigation and adaptation to climate change, resilience to disasters, and develop and implement, in line with the Sendai Framework for Disaster Risk Reduction 2015–2030, holistic disaster risk management at all levels. > Adoption and implementation of integrated solutions to climate change and resilience to disasters.`,
        sdg11_un_target_11_6_label: `Meta ONU 11.6:`,
        sdg11_un_target_11_6_text: `Reduce the environmental impacts of cities (UN definition) : By 2030, reduce the adverse per capita environmental impact of cities, including by paying special attention to air quality and municipal and other waste management. > Solid waste management. > Actions to fight urban air pollution reduction.`,
        sdg11_un_target_11_7_label: `Meta ONU 11.7:`,
        sdg11_un_target_11_7_text: `Provide access to safe and inclusive green and public spaces (UN definition) : By 2030, provide universal access to safe, inclusive and accessible, green and public spaces, in particular for women and children, older persons and persons with disabilities. > Acces to green and public spaces`,
