        sdg12_un_target_12_4_label: `Meta ONU 12.4:`,
        sdg12_un_target_12_4_text: `Responsible management of chemicals and waste : By 2020, achieve the environmentally sound management of chemicals and all wastes throughout their life cycle, in accordance with agreed international frameworks, and significantly reduce their release to air, water and soil in order to minimize their adverse impacts on human health and the environment.`,
        sdg12_un_target_12_5_label: `Meta ONU 12.5:`,
        sdg12_un_target_12_5_text: `Waste reduction : By 2030, substantially reduce waste generation through prevention, reduction, recycling, and reuse.`,
        sdg12_un_target_12_6_label: `Meta ONU 12.6:`,
        sdg12_un_target_12_6_text: `Encourage companies, especially large and transnational companies, to adopt sustainable practices and to integrate sustainability information into their reporting cycle.`,
        sdg12_un_target_12_7_label: `Meta ONU 12.7:`,
        sdg12_un_target_12_7_text: `Promote sustainable public procurement practices : Promote public procurement practices that are sustainable, in accordance with national policies and priorities.`,
        sdg12_un_target_12_8_label: `Meta ONU 12.8:`,
        sdg12_un_target_12_8_text: `By 2030 ensure that people everywhere have the relevant information and awareness for sustainable development and lifestyles in harmony with nature`,
        sdg12_un_target_12_b_label: `Meta ONU 12.b:`,
        sdg12_un_target_12_b_text: `Sustainable Tourism : Develop and implement tools to monitor sustainable development impacts for sustainable tourism which creates jobs, promotes local culture and products.`,
        sdg12_uia_criteria_label: `CRITÉRIOS ODS UIA IC / Ações:`,
        sdg12_uia_action_labeling: `> INTEGRATE THE OPERATION INTO A NATIONAL (OR INTERNATIONAL IF NOT EXISTING OR NOT DEMANDING ENOUGH) REGULATORY AND/OR LABELLING PROCESS (LEVEL's, …)`,
