        sdg12_uia_action_waste: `> ESTABLISH – FOR THE PROJECT - MEASURES TO REDUCE WASTE AND TO PROMOTE RECYCLING (INCLUDING DEPOLLUTION).`,
        sdg12_uia_action_procurement: `> IN CLOSE COLLABORATION WITH THE CLIENT USE PROCEDURES FOLLOWING PUBLIC PROCUREMENT PRACTICES THAT ARE IN ACCORDANCE WITH NATIONAL ENVIRONMENTAL POLICIES AND PRIORITIES... OR MEET THE SAME REQUIREMENTS IN THE CASE OF PRIVATE (NON PUBLIC) PROCUREMENT.`,
        sdg12_uia_action_company_practices: `> IN CLOSE COLLABORATION WITH THE CLIENT USE PROCEDURES THAT ENCOURAGE - IF NOT IMPOSE - COMPANIES TO ADOPT SUSTAINABLE PRACTICES AND SUSTAINABILITY REPORTING.`,
        sdg12_uia_action_user_info: `> IN CLOSE COLLABORATION WITH THE CLIENT MAKE SURE COSTUMERS HAVE ACCESS TO RELEVANT INFORMATION TO MAKE THE MOST OF THE PROPOSED ENVIRONMENTAL SOLUTIONS IMPLEMENTED ("INSTRUCTIONS FOR USE OF THE BUILDING", CONSUMPTION MONITORING, EQUIPMENT MAINTENANCE, ...).`,
