        sdg15_q2_option_other: `Outro / Não Aplicável`,
        sdg15_comments_label: `COMENTÁRIO: Descreva brevemente as soluções adotadas.`,
        sdg16_title: `ODS 16: PAZ, JUSTIÇA E INSTITUIÇÕES EFICAZES`,
        sdg16_subtitle: `Promover sociedades pacíficas e inclusivas, proporcionar acesso à justiça para todos!`,
        sdg16_un_targets_title: `Metas ONU & Indicadores aplicáveis em Arquitetura / ODS 16 :`,
        sdg16_un_target_16_3_label: `Meta ONU 16.3:`,
        sdg16_un_target_16_3_text: `Promote the rule of law at the national and international levels and ensure equal access to justice for all. UN Indicator 16.3.3 is proportion of the population who have experienced a dispute in the past two years and who accessed a formal or informal dispute resolution mechanism, by type of mechanism.`,
        sdg16_un_target_16_4_label: `Meta ONU 16.4:`,
        sdg16_un_target_16_4_text: `By 2030, significantly reduce illicit financial and arms flows, strengthen the recovery and return of stolen assets and combat all forms of organized crime.`,
        sdg16_un_target_16_5_label: `Meta ONU 16.5:`,
        sdg16_un_target_16_5_text: `Substantially reduce corruption and bribery in all their forms.`,
        sdg16_un_target_16_6_label: `Meta ONU 16.6:`,
        sdg16_un_target_16_6_text: `Develop effective, accountable and transparent institutions at all levels`,
        sdg16_un_target_16_7_label: `Meta ONU 16.7:`,
        sdg16_un_target_16_7_text: `Ensure responsive, inclusive, participatory and representative decision-making at all levels`,
        sdg16_un_target_16_8_label: `Meta ONU 16.8:`,
        sdg16_un_target_16_8_text: `International Governance : Broaden and strengthen the participation of developing countries in the institutions of global governance`,
        sdg16_un_target_16_b_label: `Meta ONU 16.B:`,
        sdg16_un_target_16_b_text: `Promote and enforce non-discriminatory laws and policies for sustainable development.`,
        sdg16_uia_criteria_label: `CRITÉRIOS ODS UIA IC / Ações:`,
        sdg16_uia_action_safety_walk: `> PROTECTIONS SO THAT POPULATION FEEL SAFES WALKING AROUND ALONE IN THE PLACE THEY LIVE.... WHEN NEEDED.`,
        sdg16_uia_action_safety_home: `> PROTECTIONS SO THAT POPULATION FEEL SAFES INSIDE THEIR HOME ( ACTIONS AGAINST ROBBERY, PHYSICAL AND SEXUAL ASSAULT, ...) ... WHEN NEEDED.`,
        sdg16_uia_action_legal: `> ACT WITHIN A LEGAL/ CONTRACTUAL FRAMEWORK GUARANTEEING RIGHTS TO ALL PARTIES EXCLUDING ALL FORMS OF CORRUPTION AT ALL LEVELS`,
        sdg16_uia_action_satisfaction: `> PROCEDURE TO ENSURE CUSTOMER AND USER SATISFACTION`,
        sdg16_uia_action_claims: `> ESTABLISH OPEN AND TRANSPARENT CONSENSUS STRUCTURES TO ANSWER AND PROVIDE A FAIR ANSWER TO ALL TYPES OF CLAIMS (contractors, users, neighborhood, ...) DURING THE CONSTRUCTION SITE`,
        sdg16_main_question_intro: `Actions to promote peaceful and inclusive societies for sustainable development, provide access to justice for all and build effective, accountable and inclusive institutions during the project ... such as :`,
        sdg16_feature_safety_walk: `- Integration in the project - from the design stage -effective elements (lighting, visibility, ...) so that population feel safes walking around alone in the place they live.... when needed.`,
        sdg16_feature_safety_home: `- Integration in the project - from the design stage -effective protections ( anti-burglary door and shutter system, ...) so that users feel safes inside their home ... when needed.`,
        sdg16_feature_legal: `- Implement and respect procedures to ensure that the operation will take place within a legal/ contractual framework guaranteeing rights to all parties excluding all forms of corruption at all levels.`,
        sdg16_feature_claims: `- Implement and respect procedures to establish open and transparent consensus structures to answer and provide a fair answer to all types of claims (contractors, users, neighborhood, ...) during the construction site.`,
        sdg16_feature_satisfaction: `- Establish procedures for assessing client and user satisfaction throughout and/or at the end of the project (Quality Management System).`,
        sdg16_summary_question: `Based on the aspects listed above, how many are actively addressed?`,
        sdg16_summary_instruction: `Selecione a resposta que corresponde to your project ... apenas uma escolha possível:`,
        sdg16_summary_option_0: `No specific measure taken to promote peaceful and inclusive societies and institutions ...`,
        sdg16_summary_option_1: `1 of the listed points is respected`,
        sdg16_summary_option_2: `2 of the listed points are respected`,
