        sdg16_comments_label: `COMENTÁRIO: Descreva brevemente as soluções adotadas.`,
        sdg17_title: `ODS 17: PARCERIAS E MEIOS DE IMPLEMENTAÇÃO`,
        sdg17_subtitle: `Fortalecer os meios de implementação e revitalizar a parceria global para o desenvolvimento sustentável!`,
        sdg17_un_targets_title: `Metas ONU & Indicadores aplicáveis em Arquitetura / ODS 17 :`,
        sdg17_un_target_17_6_label: `Meta ONU 17.6:`,
        sdg17_un_target_17_6_text: `Enhance North-South, South-South and triangular regional and international cooperation on and access to science, technology and innovation and enhance knowledge sharing on mutually agreed terms, including through improved coordination among existing mechanisms, in particular at the United Nations level, and through a global technology facilitation mechanism.`,
        sdg17_un_target_17_14_label: `Meta ONU 17.14:`,
        sdg17_un_target_17_14_text: `Enhance policy coherence for sustainable development.`,
        sdg17_un_target_17_15_label: `Meta ONU 17.15:`,
        sdg17_un_target_17_15_text: `Respect each country's policy space and leadership to establish and implement policies for poverty eradication and sustainable development.`,
        sdg17_un_target_17_16_label: `Meta ONU 17.16:`,
        sdg17_un_target_17_16_text: `Enhance the global partnership for sustainable development complemented by multi-stakeholder partnerships that mobilize and share knowledge, expertise, technologies and financial resources to support the achievement of sustainable development goals in all countries, particularly developing countries,`,
        sdg17_un_target_17_17_label: `Meta ONU 17.17:`,
        sdg17_un_target_17_17_text: `Encourage and promote effective public, public-private and civil society partnerships, building on the experience and resourcing strategies of partnerships,`,
        sdg17_un_target_17_18_label: `Meta ONU 17.18:`,
        sdg17_un_target_17_18_text: `By 2020, enhance capacity-building support to developing countries, including for least developed countries and small island developing States, to increase significantly the availability of high-quality, timely and reliable data disaggregated by income, gender, age, race, ethnicity, migratory status, disability, geographic location and other characteristics relevant in national contexts.`,
        sdg17_un_target_17_19_label: `Meta ONU 17.19:`,
        sdg17_un_target_17_19_text: `By 2030, build on existing initiatives to develop measurements of progress on sustainable development that complement gross domestic product, and support statistical capacity-building in developing countries`,
        sdg17_uia_criteria_label: `CRITÉRIOS ODS UIA IC / Ações:`,
        sdg17_uia_action_cooperation: `> THE OPERATION IS BEING CARRIED OUT UNDER A COOPERATION PROGRAMME L (NORTH-SOUTH, SOUTH-SOUTH AND TRIANGULAR REGIONAL AND INTERNATIONAL).`,
        sdg17_uia_action_national_goals: `> THE PROJECT RESPECT (MINIMUM) NATIONAL GOALS SET UP TO IMPLEMENT THE SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT GOALS.`,
        sdg17_uia_action_initiatives: `> THE OPERATION GAVE RISE TO INITIATIVES TO :`,
        sdg17_uia_action_sharing: `- SHARE DATA AND KNOWLEDGE ABOUT TECHNIQUES IMPROVEMENTS AND/OR INNOVATIONS, CONCEPTUAL OR PROGRAMMATIC APPROACHES DEVELOPED THROUGH CONFERENCES, TECHNICAL PUBLICATIONS, VOCATIONAL TRAINING, WORKSHOP, ETC.,`,
        sdg17_uia_action_partnership: `- TO BUILD OR REVITALIZE GLOBAL PARTNERSHIP FOR SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT (PARTNERSHIP, FINANCIAL SUPPORT, ...).`,
        sdg17_uia_action_team: `> SET UP - AROUND THE ARCHITECT - A MULTIDISCIPLINARY TEAM COMPRISING ALL THE INGENUITIES TO RESPOND WITH RELEVANCE TO ALL THE ISSUES RAISED BY THE PROJECT.`,
        sdg17_uia_action_reporting: `> PROJECT ENVIRONMENTAL DATA WERE MEASURED AND REPORTED AT THE NATIONAL (OR REGIONAL) LEVEL TO DEVELOP MEASUREMENTS OF PROGRESS ON SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT THAT COMPLEMENT GROSS DOMESTIC PRODUCT.`,
        sdg17_main_question_intro: `WHAT ACTIONS WERE BE TAKEN ON THIS PROJECT TO REVITALIZE THE GLOBAL PARTNERSHIP FOR SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT :`,
        sdg17_feature_cooperation: `- The operation is part of an international cooperation programme, an experimental sustainable development project, ...`,
        sdg17_feature_goals: `- The project respect (at least) the national /regional sustainable development goals.`,
        sdg17_feature_sharing: `- The operation gave rise to initiatives to : share data and knowledge (publications, conferences,...).`,
        sdg17_feature_partnership: `- The operation gave rise to initiatives to : to build or revitalize global partnership between professionals in the building sector (architects, engineers, product and equipment manufacturers, developers, entrepreneurs, ...).`,
        sdg17_feature_team: `- A multidisciplinary team - as wide as necessary - was set up to respond with relevance to all the issues raised by the project.`,
        sdg17_feature_reporting: `> Project environmental data were measured and reported - at the national (or regional) level - to develop progress on sustainable development.`,
        sdg17_summary_question: `Based on the aspects listed above, how many are actively addressed?`,
        sdg17_summary_instruction: `Selecione a resposta que corresponde to your project ... apenas uma escolha possível:`,
        sdg17_summary_option_0: `No specific measure taken to promote peaceful and inclusive societies and institutions ...`,
